  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This NZD 2.5 million activity will consolidate 3 areas of support to Tuvalu for fiscal and public sector strengthening:
&lt;ul&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Policy Reform Matrix budget support, NZD 1 million;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Tuvalu Trust Fund, NZD 1 million;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Support the Tuvalu Trust Fund, its committees, and Board through the provision of advisory services; and&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;Support scoping and design work to identify opportunities for New&#xA0;Zealand to more effectively support Tuvalu to strengthen its fiscal environment and improve public service delivery.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;</narrative>
